<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
    <title>숙소 상세 - Forest Haven</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts & Icons -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-light pb-5">
    <div class="fh-wrapper">
        <header class="fh-navbar bg-white bg-opacity-80 backdrop-blur-md sticky-top">
            <div class="navbar-brand">
                <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn-icon me-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
                <h2 class="brand-name">숙소 상세</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                <button class="btn-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">share</span></button>
                <button class="btn-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">favorite</span></button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="container py-5 content-inner-max">
            <!-- Hero Carousel -->
            <section class="mb-5">
                <div id="roomCarousel" class="carousel slide shadow-lg rounded-4 overflow-hidden" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-indicators">
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#roomCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#roomCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#roomCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBZ4ctAyqdw3ME68w9psGPbwAVD14PaaoeBGrbRbNFxrFN2YcW-g1QQzfIMLRioBkI7105rTyTwUUq64f2q6MQS-SD_fSYycpVdyxoIjiZOPEp5rH_WjNTOybUszI_o0tgUO_Oc4UYV7CTKDTzKWsCQyDG8usppaiAn_TkuzWbQouHSr796L-kKx-Fe12JOu5yitFjZqQuEiT1HZpCweW4Cr3a1NnY9SLsLcPr21Ws8EkCpWrO3l-b_SwX9cvHl-DFq0yjgzHbkgML0" alt="Main View">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAUYJDRHg382aRAR6yDQAkWM6NRxtjq_aLExtaXGen9-iPJXGUX4pRy4sFS0ALOzSPZedWEK7bsfWCwl29eA28UTkC57BNMxAwT2Q7iHwOWzhHNb9m_oBCnvGupFepwcWvwDIoY6g4D5-nDPLRElHNp3GUeBP2l8kEUKsAARmffK0oRGi9FkiLumFDRopi3D2-IGguvFeqlAXPiBbzSlalxAYt15C4lHV60BLaQlVbECYxmKOncP9_9wgbVecp_CwifvlrB3HBsLwNL" alt="Interior">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA9C7dPMlBSbw9A8NH20fT3H2SldTeFPvnsHrAgQIcaJPn3Mqh9LyzDRXaNStZYUgYjvcG4Qq9UEFoTYzwdBac2nVIOZCkazyaDxECaConns1iUa8_A2uzSTs0x60G0riP-78-zMiZXMDbxX0tIEHdj17T45AB9ZcSoXth3VlkjgdPpGYYZSpCqWNzkoBb2s2OJkrqauzNLHnaCGtswcoH0rA25DvFnmv-9wxYm02qOKAv_hSx3f5PfXuxBZnBfjYy4Amv8J_1I7N9K" alt="Night View">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#roomCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <div class="carousel-btn-circle"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_left</span></div>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#roomCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                        <div class="carousel-btn-circle"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span></div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Room Titles -->
            <section class="mb-5">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-end mb-3">
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="display-5 fw-black text-primary mb-2">A-1 데크 (Forest View)</h1>
                        <p class="text-secondary fw-medium fs-5 m-0">탁 트인 전망과 프라이빗한 휴식 공간</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end">
                        <p class="text-secondary small fw-bold mb-1">리뷰 평점</p>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 text-primary fw-black fs-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span> 4.9
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr class="opacity-10">
            </section>

            <!-- Details Grid -->
            <section class="row g-4 mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="fh-card p-4 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center shadow-sm border-0 bg-white rounded-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary fs-4">group</span>
                            <span class="text-secondary small fw-bold">수용 인원</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="fw-black text-dark">기준 2인 / 최대 4인</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="fh-card p-4 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center shadow-sm border-0 bg-white rounded-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary fs-4">payments</span>
                            <span class="text-secondary small fw-bold">1박 요금</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="fw-black text-primary fs-5">150,000원 ~</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Amenities -->
            <section class="mb-5">
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-dark mb-4 d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">grid_view</span> 편의 시설
                </h3>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-5 text-primary fw-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">와이파이</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-5 text-primary fw-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">에어컨</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-5 text-primary fw-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">전용 데크</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-5 text-primary fw-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">바비큐 그릴</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-5 text-primary fw-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">전기차 충전</span>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Reviews -->
            <section class="mb-5 border-top pt-5">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5">
                    <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-dark m-0 d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">rate_review</span> 이용 후기 <span class="text-primary small">24</span>
                    </h3>
                    <button class="btn btn-light bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 text-secondary btn-sm fw-bold px-3 border-0 opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed">후기 작성</button>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4">
                    <!-- Review 1 -->
                    <div class="review-item-card shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD-8SjLr_TceFQBu-_rwYPbUL52etA-_UsL9Gg8hoGe_GmQtwNwoPpCIqx6YhCr4S43ozkSCslrnr09vT6dqqcvG2aCFXJCny4VN5DbbZ_8iRndHdrvtLY4klxxBvvm9dTwaeut4yVrLoFBgNFl9zGM0r6IDiA7CDrNe1D1-q2vYWtbjFWbe2WAcM6KZs06ay93sNsp7PD8cRTY9PIsMbpYHc2Hmd2GCEp9h1xAiBfOX8Azhv33sOiTtHc3iAxBO15VDCV1v5NabuFh" class="review-user-img shadow-sm" alt="User">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="small fw-bold text-dark m-0">김*준</p>
                                    <div class="rating-stars text-warning d-flex">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span>
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span>
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span>
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span>
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-fill-1">star</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-secondary opacity-50 fw-bold fs-xxs">2023.10.24</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-secondary small leading-relaxed mb-3">데크가 정말 넓고 뷰가 환상적입니다. 아침에 안개 낀 산 풍경을 보면서 커피 한 잔 하니 세상 행복하네요. 시설도 깨끗하게 잘 관리되어 있습니다.</p>
                        <div class="review-photo-list d-flex gap-2">
                            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAXOhGfH7LR9jgbs_l76sxDb2LiuyNhgTkShnxjdanvr1kQs8r3V6dHT1Luxhiuk1j-TDs_vSV7ws0c_-0GOsIv4C0uZYa7lvPi0Y6NEEZU2VQg1Bkn6L7lQaJdbGXIcztvvxj2sgm_2Mrs2YrjpgSv0sVQdXXdKqILfNYRNT7ZISEx5lYpFUA9Jn0KXcwfNpV8ozpIJg8LXhdacRg7yoF6OJVDrtLu83Rp2DbE8QDHCaF11LViCHaD2wHaOd_VKSoIaCatQNOU6ee2" alt="Review Photo">
                            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA9C7dPMlBSbw9A8NH20fT3H2SldTeFPvnsHrAgQIcaJPn3Mqh9LyzDRXaNStZYUgYjvcG4Qq9UEFoTYzwdBac2nVIOZCkazyaDxECaConns1iUa8_A2uzSTs0x60G0riP-78-zMiZXMDbxX0tIEHdj17T45AB9ZcSoXth3VlkjgdPpGYYZSpCqWNzkoBb2s2OJkrqauzNLHnaCGtswcoH0rA25DvFnmv-9wxYm02qOKAv_hSx3f5PfXuxBZnBfjYy4Amv8J_1I7N9K" alt="Review Photo">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <!-- Fixed Bottom Bar -->
        <div class="fixed-bottom-bar shadow-lg">
            <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center content-inner-max">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                    <span class="text-secondary fw-bold fs-xxs">1박 기준 요금</span>
                    <span class="h4 fw-black text-primary m-0">150,000원~</span>
                </div>
                <button onclick="location.href='/reservations/new'" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5 py-3 fw-black shadow-lg border-0 rounded-3">실시간 예약하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
